{"tid":410843,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"想問下呢個算唔算係受禁制武器","createTime":"2017-09-23T09:48:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-23T11:14:56.000Z","uid":16465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b32ce75682ce5ba157c544ff23b22a5e71be5b5e","tid":410843,"uid":16465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T09:48:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/23/174811_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F23%2F174811_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=1e40a935&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ee72257e8a87226aec47fecb147d26169731d209","tid":410843,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T09:49:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5d609a9bbc2b2d62bbc7637d3f30be1ba6524a1e","tid":410843,"uid":16465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T09:51:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>菲律賓魔杖就唔算</blockquote><br />\n唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2164841f7e7e1c30ea9724d0c8fdfa1516e8cc2","tid":410843,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T10:13:51.000Z","msg":"紅底咪唔算"},{"pid":"4db63478b7cf18d9e1cb96deb009c4bb24926c42","tid":410843,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T10:14:26.000Z","msg":"唔係紅底<br />\n波都係武器啦"},{"pid":"d89f47a4897543ff5c4f68c0222f275c2e9c0d45","tid":410843,"uid":30510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T10:16:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/7i94kh3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F7i94kh3.png&h=742a65fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n生果刀都得啦<br />\n如果你鍾意食榴槤"},{"pid":"0ef3a1ca037902b26be85cab5d86f695c4f1e2d4","tid":410843,"uid":119330,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T10:17:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/23/174811_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F23%2F174811_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=1e40a935&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n根據香港法例217章《武器條例》第4條，任何人管有違禁武器，均屬犯罪。<br />\n<br />\n根據香港法例217章《武器條例》，違禁武器包括: <br />\n中國式飛鏢<br />\n重力刀<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">重力操作鋼棒</span><br />\n指節套，不論是否有尖釘及是否有刀刃<br />\n附有手柄的鐵鏈<br />\n彈簧鋼棒<br />\n任何以彈簧或其他機械或電動裝置露出刀刃的刀<br />\n任何有刀刃或尖端的武器，其設計是在使用時以拳頭緊握手柄，而刀刃或尖端則從拳頭指縫間突出<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根據條例<br />\n其實算係受禁制武器"},{"pid":"cc60cf833eecfe5b1a4986c9c1c3e646561610c1","tid":410843,"uid":30510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T10:19:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/23/174811_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F23%2F174811_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=1e40a935&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n根據香港法例217章《武器條例》第4條，任何人管有違禁武器，均屬犯罪。<br />\n<br />\n根據香港法例217章《武器條例》，違禁武器包括: <br />\n中國式飛鏢<br />\n重力刀<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">重力操作鋼棒</span><br />\n指節套，不論是否有尖釘及是否有刀刃<br />\n附有手柄的鐵鏈<br />\n彈簧鋼棒<br />\n任何以彈簧或其他機械或電動裝置露出刀刃的刀<br />\n任何有刀刃或尖端的武器，其設計是在使用時以拳頭緊握手柄，而刀刃或尖端則從拳頭指縫間突出<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根據條例<br />\n其實算係受禁制武器</blockquote><br />\n唔用鋼造咪得"},{"pid":"f92956168edfd890241dc83ecda3634ca0a82fe0","tid":410843,"uid":12021,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T10:19:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1f7195e88f651c653eba9288db7209f198ee366a","tid":410843,"uid":119330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T11:05:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/23/174811_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F23%2F174811_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=1e40a935&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n根據香港法例217章《武器條例》第4條，任何人管有違禁武器，均屬犯罪。<br />\n<br />\n根據香港法例217章《武器條例》，違禁武器包括: <br />\n中國式飛鏢<br />\n重力刀<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">重力操作鋼棒</span><br />\n指節套，不論是否有尖釘及是否有刀刃<br />\n附有手柄的鐵鏈<br />\n彈簧鋼棒<br />\n任何以彈簧或其他機械或電動裝置露出刀刃的刀<br />\n任何有刀刃或尖端的武器，其設計是在使用時以拳頭緊握手柄，而刀刃或尖端則從拳頭指縫間突出<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根據條例<br />\n其實算係受禁制武器</blockquote><br />\n返去含撚啦，碌野邊有重力操作機關？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你search 下乜野係重力操作鋼棒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw 我屌你老母臭閪 文盲就唔該死撚開啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ffff813e56519a34318a720f2ea9bebbf5e395e","tid":410843,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T11:14:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}